1)compatiable version download for hbase-hadoop  (Take hbase-0.90.6 or 0.94.0 	version)

2)Copy hadoop-core*.jar, common-configuration*.jar,
 common-collection*.jar  from hadoop ---> hbase/lib/ 

3) Copy hdfs-site.xml from hadoop/conf/ ---> hbase/conf/

4) Configure hbase-site.xml accordingly

5) comment if there is any 127.0.1.1 in /etc/hosts